For ubuntu:

Pakages to be installed before compiling:

sudo apt-get install freeglut3 freeglut3-dev qt5-default cmake  libxmu-dev libxi-dev mesa-common-dev libgl1-mesa-dev

There are some problems for installing. If there is a broken link to EGL and GL
libraries, execute:

sudo rm /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libEGL.so; sudo ln /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libEGL.so.1 /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libEGL.so

sudo rm /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libGL.so; sudo ln /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libGL.so.1 /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libGL.so


